Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a move on, Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.16,0:00:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ed, slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The library isn't going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're a bunch of slowpokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's acting like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I beg your pardon. He is a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ed, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.32,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ed. Can you go anywhere\Nwithout plowing into people?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, yes, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, are you going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Never been better!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going, Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter, Ed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.32,0:01:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Central, here we come!
